a) requires the consultants for Terminal Operation, Local Economic Enterprise and Bulk Water and Port Operation Facilities submit to the Audit Team their deliverables like the comprehensive business plan and physical report of operations for their assigned economic enterprise or the operational plan as stipulated in the Contract of Service;

b) submit  copy of the Contract of Services of the Financial Consultant to the Audit Team;

We recommended that the Local Finance Committee prepares the financial reports for the economic enterprise of the LGU and conduct the semi-annual financial self-sufficiency review for evaluation by the Municipal Mayor and Sangguniang Bayan.

